# 2Ô∏è‚É£0Ô∏è‚É£ Summary

| Term | Meaning |
|------|----------|
| SCM | Manage source code |
| Git | Version tool |
| VCS | Track changes |
| Branch | Separate work |
| Commit | Save |
| Push | Upload |
| Pull | Download |
| Merge | Combine |
| SSH | Secure login |
